results/

# F4.4 slide_calibration round artifacts — commit the small text artifacts so
# rounds are reproducible + comparable from git history; exclude PDFs (4-5 MB
# each) and the seeded-session-ids cache (per-developer local state).
!slide_calibration/results/
!slide_calibration/results/round_*/
!slide_calibration/results/round_*/**/
# Re-exclude what shouldn't be committed (the `**/` rule above re-includes
# every file in the round tree; these lines knock the binary + local-state
# files back out):
slide_calibration/results/_sessions.json
slide_calibration/results/round_*/**/*.pdf
